title: Weber Stainless 3-Piece Barbecue Tool Set 306630 - Overview
description:
Weber Stainless 3-Piece Barbecue Tool Set - 306630 
http://www.abt.com/product/59660/Weber-306630.html

Tong handle locks for compact storage. The spatulas angled neck reaches over the edge of the grill keeping your hands and arms away from the heat. The fork tines are designed to pierce food without shredding it.
Features:
• Tong handle locks for compact storage
• Spatulas angled neck reaches over the edge of the grill
• The fork tines are designed to pierce food without shredding it
• Set includes spatula tongs and fork
